  <brief_title>A Safety and Tolerability Study of REGN88(SAR153191) in Subjects With Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-dose, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel Group Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacodynamic Study of Subcutaneous REGN88 in Subjects With Rheumatoid Arthritis Receiving Concomitant Methotrexate</official_title>
