  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single-dose, double-blind, placebo-controlled, parallel group safety, tolerability
      and pharmacodynamic study of subcutaneously (SC) administered REGN88 in rheumatoid arthritis
      patients who are receiving concomitant methotrexate. Four (4) parallel groups of 8 subjects
      each with active rheumatoid arthritis will be dosed SC.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
